e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T20:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽聞有人叫佢做過渡期？ 過咗呢個階段就可以過世<br />\n利申 未試過 唔知</blockquote><br />\n點樣可以過到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係等時間過<br />\n而係你要著手搵個問題既源頭出黎<br />\n再兩個人一齊努力去配合/協調/承諾</blockquote><br />\n冇用架，講完唔夠兩日打回原型</blockquote><br />\n咁即係 無承諾/做唔到<br />\n<br />\n變相可以話其實唔夠決心去改善<br />\n伴侶既關係同個人習慣相比<br />\n佢似乎會更重視佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bb62458afe3f0def205f2770e8acb9768d9220","tid":183103,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T20:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽聞有人叫佢做過渡期？ 過咗呢個階段就可以過世<br />\n利申 未試過 唔知</blockquote><br />\n點樣可以過到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係等時間過<br />\n而係你要著手搵個問題既源頭出黎<br />\n再兩個人一齊努力去配合/協調/承諾</blockquote><br />\n問佢咩事又話無野 可以點？"},{"pid":"9359557d9783613459aa73d2e041569505d3dbc1","tid":183103,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T20:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽聞有人叫佢做過渡期？ 過咗呢個階段就可以過世<br />\n利申 未試過 唔知</blockquote><br />\n點樣可以過到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係等時間過<br />\n而係你要著手搵個問題既源頭出黎<br />\n再兩個人一齊努力去配合/協調/承諾</blockquote><br />\n問佢咩事又話無野 可以點？</blockquote><br />\n問佢就死都話無事<br />\n但其實你明明就 feel 到有野<br />\n但佢話無，唔肯講<br />\n就會抹煞埋你唯一可以解決個問題既方法<br />\n慢慢就會覺得大家都有所隱瞞，無放個心出黎<br />\n覺得距離感增加，但又無從解決<br />\n最後必然分手<br />\n<br />\n可以點<br />\n同佢講清楚你既感受<br />\n當你知道佢有野唔講既時候，其實你既心入面會諗啲咩野<br />\n會好無助，會懷疑係咪自己做得唔好<br />\n會好唔開心，但又唔知可以點做<br />\n呢啲感覺會一直一直咁積累<br />\n得唔到解決遲啲就會好易分手<br />\n你唔想咁，你想一有問題出現就即刻解決左佢<br />\n你希望會同佢一齊繼續行落去<br />\n所以希望佢會有咩都拎出黎講<br />\n咁當然你都要咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n如果講清楚哂講埋後果，唔拎出黎講就會散<br />\n而佢都唔肯講既<br />\n咁佢應該係想散多過想一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37d1d7037b919cc629b8cc84f6694bd2ab3322d","tid":183103,"uid":92902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T21:21:24.000Z","msg":"明知大家性格火星撞地球一星期at least嘈一獲 都因為唔捨得散又一齊返又散又一齊返十幾廿次 諗起都覺得自己on9 散左先發覺浪費左既時間買唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950fa1e450928bff69551c060689b2c4f0dd2893","tid":183103,"uid":1911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T21:22:43.000Z","msg":"我好愛你"},{"pid":"12ecd64c6d5212adc94feafbc935e111140ad428","tid":183103,"uid":63454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T21:24:36.000Z","msg":"到你真係分開 你又會唔捨得"},{"pid":"96cd6e49d79582530a51a8e09e640584bd4f5b59","tid":183103,"uid":63454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T21:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到你真係分開 你又會唔捨得</blockquote><br />\n應該話 冇得你唔捨得 利申過來人"},{"pid":"b91a5eebd860f8fdc14aac7e294ad17069d232c6","tid":183103,"uid":44048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:09:57.000Z","msg":"試過 岩岩散左<br />\n好想解決但都解決唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcb88768e7253e74b9b8e350f7ab4f39194819c","tid":183103,"uid":7664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過 岩岩散左<br />\n好想解決但都解決唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解決唔到d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b3089c1ebbde1db5903708fdbd22dad60114c9cd","tid":183103,"uid":44048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過 岩岩散左<br />\n好想解決但都解決唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解決唔到d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帽左 之後佢番黎<br />\n之後都係行唔到落去<br />\n佢話對住我只有內疚同唔捨得好辛苦"},{"pid":"4d4387062fd62b9b572d88ea08df21d6f9e76b09","tid":183103,"uid":7664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過 岩岩散左<br />\n好想解決但都解決唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解決唔到d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帽左 之後佢番黎<br />\n之後都係行唔到落去<br />\n佢話對住我只有內疚同唔捨得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n你會唔會等佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcde4fc7290042133b4347583ae4e0962cee7eab","tid":183103,"uid":44048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過 岩岩散左<br />\n好想解決但都解決唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n解決唔到d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帽左 之後佢番黎<br />\n之後都係行唔到落去<br />\n佢話對住我只有內疚同唔捨得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n你會唔會等佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<br />\n就算我等佢都未必會番黎<br />\n我都好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前一齊住 而家日日自己<br />\n唔知點面對"},{"pid":"768f2c1ee42179eec56e15d3e485ac7fd573417e","tid":183103,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"雖然可悲，但都係賤。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f544ef555a18171fed71a36136177c272f656c","tid":183103,"uid":79093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:57:24.000Z","ms