fcbddf18cc3a5feff4a3f340","tid":183103,"uid":87711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"其實唔捨得同愛有冇分別 如果又愛又唔愛咁仲有冇得掹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9fc2892f14c1d716f2c1c105492603a939c0e7","tid":183103,"uid":72967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"試過 最後拍左5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為某d原因鼓起勇氣割捨"},{"pid":"78028a28e81c5e741ee031c72c6aba4655103c1a","tid":183103,"uid":74805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"唔好再拖 唔好害人"},{"pid":"fa5b78892e38eb31d57412656a2ccca1b759bb8b","tid":183103,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T03:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔捨得同愛有冇分別 如果又愛又唔愛咁仲有冇得掹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有分別，好大分別添<br />\n<br />\n愛佢既你會為佢做好多野<br />\n會讓步會改<br />\n<br />\n唔捨得會逃避"},{"pid":"407718f06be898311512acdb2bda0fb3984af20f","tid":183103,"uid":87711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔捨得同愛有冇分別 如果又愛又唔愛咁仲有冇得掹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有分別，好大分別添<br />\n<br />\n愛佢既你會為佢做好多野<br />\n會讓步會改<br />\n<br />\n唔捨得會逃避</blockquote><br />\n咁係咪已經冇得掹⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話唔捨得分手 又唔知自己想點 但話同我一齊又好自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話咩想一段關係入面得開心 唔洗嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我夠想啦 但如果係咁 仲叫做拍拖咩<br />\nsorry for1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4eb76d052c456e34d7f5afbd5edf8b907726a1","tid":183103,"uid":92902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識左五年，拍左半年，隔日嘈交<br />\n以為係大家唔成熟又以為嘈交只係我地之間一個比較特別既生活方式<br />\n明明大家都仲愛大家唔想放手，但係一直相處只係一日比一日唔鍾意，仲憎佢<br />\n本身都話分手，但係唔捨得<br />\n估唔到咁快行到呢步，行到呢步，冇架啦，都係分手</blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好明白你巴打 我同ex又係成日嘈但又唔捨得散 不過咁樣始終相處唔到落去 3年都照散"},{"pid":"f4b6e1593b866a1b8262078c6bd5437cc8fbf8a5","tid":183103,"uid":75026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54d59f931d0e5bd063f7b5741774e981a6c6d19b","tid":183103,"uid":87711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識左五年，拍左半年，隔日嘈交<br />\n以為係大家唔成熟又以為嘈交只係我地之間一個比較特別既生活方式<br />\n明明大家都仲愛大家唔想放手，但係一直相處只係一日比一日唔鍾意，仲憎佢<br />\n本身都話分手，但係唔捨得<br />\n估唔到咁快行到呢步，行到呢步，冇架啦，都係分手</blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好明白你巴打 我同ex又係成日嘈但又唔捨得散 不過咁樣始終相處唔到落去 3年都照散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為佢好幫佢諗哂所有野，佢話我煩，我傷心到走左，結果佢又真係比我走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁其實如果大家都肯改 仲有冇得行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef7112ae6fc172db7dc70a3f1b75d6cf696b316","tid":183103,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"hello<br />\n呢到，對另一半係感情多<br />\n有好多原因覺得無咩可能走落去<br />\n始終佢屋企未必接受我"},{"pid":"0a424fb25484a2bacfd261b2cddd1b8b4108d13e","tid":183103,"uid":88490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"如果同完另一半講完問題 而佢又唔覺得有問題<br />\n講分手 無挽留你 仲會講你走左會好d<br />\n咁樣既人係咪唔駛要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4908f77d32b42d6ba43d3ca02cb58b4